contents.name: Discord.FM
contents.page:
A simple bot for getting statistics from Last.fm that also comes with some simple voice integrations.
While still in it's early days, Discord.FM includes the following features:
* Deep Last.fm integration to access details like scrobbles, and track info. * Self-assingable last.fm accounts * Youtube and Soundcloud integrations (including experimental voice features) * Aggressive data caching. * and more coming.
